{
  "stem": "490.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of them were dead, except me, that I was-- the rest of them were all-- we jumped out of the track, of course.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nobody survived from these six people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, one survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he lost his leg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just end up by having a few shrapnels in my arm, which I didn't even notice till I got to-- to this new camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a real muddy-- a new camp, which they built.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I got there, they told me that this camp is the worst thing you have ever experienced in life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to travel for thousands and thousands of, you know, feet down, or-- and you know, it's very unhuman conditions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- so I devised-- I-- while I was in the hospital, they said, if you can prolong your stay in the hospital as long you can do it, stay in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they-- you're better off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they're not going to do nothing to you while you're in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So every time my arm healed, I riped it off apart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took-- put salt during the night so that the wound shouldn't heal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on account of this arm that was I shot, I stayed in this hospital until I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was never-- never experienced any hardship in this camp, except we had no food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had nothing to live on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was the only camp that I knew that is the most-- the most awful place in the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I still remained there, until I was liberated by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the hospital?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there about-- at least for three months or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After Buchenwald, and then we went there, about three months I was at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spent--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
